| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6598 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6a14a1ee-f5d6-5f00-83fe-58bad4373d25"
